Red Rock West on Blu-ray

Director John Dahl's ("The Last Seduction") smart, twist-filled thriller stars Nicolas Cage as Michael Williams, a down-and-out Texan whose drifting through the American West ends in a Wyoming bar where he's mistaken for a hit man. Williams accepts a proposition from the bar owner's alluring wife (Lara Flynn Boyle) to bump off her husband, but when actual killer Lyle (Dennis Hopper) arrives in town, complications ensue. J.T. Walsh, Dwight Yoakam, Timothy Carhart co-star. 98 min. Widescreen; Soundtrack: English DTS HD stereo Master Audio; Subtitles: English (SDH); audio commentary; featurettes.
